➜【星连文学社】湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：我是你等待的牛郎
http://www.sohu.com/a/414977952_100115135	24817
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200826/af76036bdafd433882d81cef40c15bd0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我是你等待的牛郎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣(武汉)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我是你等待的牛郎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为爱，我更懂得对你尊重</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我常常清理颜容</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以勤劳汉洗躯体，用荷露清洗脑洞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只有干净才能配上瑶宫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你看，今日天空特别蓝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>探不到底的爱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>是无法计量的海</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>到底有多深，喜鹊叽叽喳喳在猜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>静流，海天河汉满满</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无须表白内心的柔软</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只要看那在天上白云的流转</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看阳光下剔透的肝胆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我对你的忠诚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">像雪一样晶莹至纯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>为了见你，我在打理自己</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
