➜【星连文学社】江西诗人时差先生：失眠者
http://www.sohu.com/a/414978633_100115135	25014
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200826/1df4612b2bcf4a6ba2426341b951ad80.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>失眠者</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/时差先生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一桶灭掉了的烟头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">产生的污浊空气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如一排排高高的烟囱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冒出来的龌龊无耻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一辆辆车子堵得发慌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个个工厂在西风中飘移</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦似乎死亡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一切都面目全非</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">狰狞的面孔扑向这沉睡的大地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有谁亮出利剑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刺穿这狗血的噱头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有这滴血淋淋的世界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灵魂在夜的表白下驱动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">迟迟不能入睡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">南方的雨烟好久不见了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸟的叫声显得苍白无力</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
