➜【星连文学社】彩虹：一低眉，花容娇羞
http://www.sohu.com/a/414994667_100115135	29494
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200826/30039158f962470795398939c82a85d6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一低眉，花容娇羞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/彩虹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水清清潺潺</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小叶叶圆圆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨柳拂面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">湖面生辉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一低眉，花容娇羞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>陪着湖水低声细语</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遍布湖岸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>如黛玉思着宝玉怜爱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>垂泪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>晨上露水小花</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>多像一串串相思泪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">湖边跑道上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三三两两，路人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一抬头，亭子和荷花</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">默然深绿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">事事非非，非非事事</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
