<p class="ql-align-center">焉知快乐否</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>此时，湖面托起，一只船</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一只竹排船，二人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打捞着什么</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>感叹号还是休止符</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>花容娇羞，躲在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>后面</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>如同鱼儿吐着一口口</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>水泡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>白天的小小月亮</strong></p>
