➜【星连文学社】臭香儿香：七夕原创组诗（存念篇）
http://www.sohu.com/a/415032905_100115135	42360
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《七夕，想你有毒》（原创）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/臭香儿香（陕西）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200826/51fca1ef216044b18976c5d3b883f4d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（一）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你是一颗流星</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无意坠落我的心湖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拼凑着你的晦涩、残骼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>亏我，还你满血复活的星火</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>燎原，我的断垣残雪——</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人将你的名字注入诗行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">残花与败柳，和诗相约</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一场又一场，拟人的风花雪月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200826/c65049b28c5445f28e33585c7393d021.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（二）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我，只是你的一个曾经</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而你，醉卧于那片薰衣草花丛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早已忘了，三月的一轮清月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又是如何抚慰一朵谷兰的凄冷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>六月，你就背叛了所有</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就像初春的新冠病毒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>如此泛滥，又，如此放纵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/7ae4d77a435649b6bc3cb5eea9d2f203.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（三）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你，永远都是一个出轨者</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那条幽深的月光小径</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">漫画着你不顾廉耻的婚外情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>天上的星星不会撒谎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>婆娑一双慧眼，偷窥着我的心酸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还有你的幽情单绪，你侬我侬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200826/5ad924a5c3cd423abf5542275f9d328c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（四）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">七夕，今夕何夕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我已无心探究</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遥望天庭，星汉辉映</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>只见牛郎，不见织女</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当你划破我的夜空</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鹊桥虽有梦，想你却有毒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我知道，从此——</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天空少了一颗星星</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">地上多了一双眼睛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/2ff97aadcfe94554bf2d716580fbbb54.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/73c2166231a541eaa532c6fdc0cdcbba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
